    <h1>NYC Referrals</h1>
    <p>
        Mindful Care believes that supplement therapy is imperative in completing the patient journey. Finding an
        appropriate therapeutic resource can be hard to do, but we are here to help! Below are some of our partnering
        resources:
    </p>

    <h3 class="main">MindFit Group Therapy</h3>

    <p>
        MindFit Group Therapy strengthens your mental health now. Therapists guide an interactive and supportive
        conversation that makes a difference for everyone. We use a CBT-based approach. Cognitive Behavioral Therapy
        (CBT) focuses on challenging and changing unhelpful thoughts, beliefs, attitudes and behaviors. CBT is a
        practical approach to improve the quality of your life.
    </p>
    <p>
        <%= link "MindFit Group Therapy", target: "_blank", to: Routes.page_path(@conn, :group_therapy) %>
    </p>

